'''鞏膜環'''（{{Lang-en|sclerotic ring}}）是[[脊椎动物|脊椎動物]]眼周的一圈骨質結構，該結構可以被發現於除現存的哺乳動物和鱷類之外的其他脊椎動物<ref name="UCMP">{{cite web|title=Eyes of Ichthyosaurs|url=http://www.ucmp.berkeley.edu/people/motani/ichthyo/eyes.html|accessdate=15 October 2013|author=|date=15 November 2001|last=Motani|first=Ryosuke|format=|publisher=UC Museum of Paleontology|language=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20011217152147/http://www.ucmp.berkeley.edu/people/motani/ichthyo/eyes.html|archive-date=17 December 2001}} </ref>。鞏膜環可能是由單一或多塊骨骼組成的<ref name=palaeos>{{cite web |url=http://palaeos.com/vertebrates/glossary/glossaryS.html |title=Palaeos Vertebrates: Glossary S |accessdate=2007-07-06 |archive-date=2012-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120217205558/http://palaeos.com/vertebrates/glossary/glossaryS.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。鞏膜環由其包圍這的[[巩膜|鞏膜]]而得名，人們認為鞏膜環在保護眼部方面發揮了重要作用，尤其是眼睛非球狀和生活現在水底的動物。鞏膜環在古生物化石中較為引人注意，如滅絕的魚龍、翼龍、恐龍等<ref name=DML>{{cite web |last=Pigdon |first=Dann |url=http://dml.cmnh.org/1997Oct/msg00393.html |title=Re: Sclerotic ring in eyes |accessdate=2007-07-06 |archive-date=2018-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180928051830/http://dml.cmnh.org/1997Oct/msg00393.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

